items: Frollo King of Sweland and conqueror of Norway.
Hasmond and Gotar, two courtiers to Frollo.
Marfisa, an humorous gentlewoman, cousin to Fatyma.
Fredericke and Wermond, two noble men of Norway.
Hubba, an humorous merry Danish Captaine.
Cowsell and Radgee, two foolish Coxcombes.
Two posts, a Scout, & two Gentl,
Achylles, and Satyres, in a maske: which may be Acted by the forenam'd persons.
